cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM. 

The paper focuses on visual relationship detection, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the proposed method involves machine learning and decision-making, which are covered by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the use of multi-modal features suggests that cs.MM (Multimedia) could also be a relevant sub-category.
